nd`\n159:   - Use: \"update NAME\"\n160:   - Flags: --image, --cpu, --memory (partial updates)\n161:   - Fetch existing, apply changes, update\n162: \n163: - [ ] **TASK-057**: Create `pkg/cli/agentruntime/delete.go`\n164:   - Implement `NewAgentRuntimeDeleteCommand(o *agentRuntimeOptions) *cobra.Command`\n165:   - Use: \"delete NAME\"\n166:   - Flags: --force, --grace-period\n167:   - Delete with confirmation prompt (unless --force)\n168: \n169: - [ ] **TASK-058**: Create `pkg/cli/agentruntime/logs.go`\n170:   - Implement `NewAgentRuntimeLogsCommand(o *agentRuntimeOptions) *cobra.Command`\n171:   - Use: \"logs NAME\"\n172:   - Flags: --follow, --tail, --since, --container\n173:   - Stream pod logs using k8s API\n174: \n175: ### Phase 7: codeinterpreter Commands (`pkg/cli/codeinterpreter/`)\n176: \n177: - [ ] **TASK-060**: Create `pkg/cli/codeinterpreter/codeinterpreter.go`\n178:   - Define `codeInterpreterOptions` struct\n179:   - Implement `NewCodeInterpreterCommand() *cobra.Command`\n180:   - Add persistent flags\n181:   - Add subcommands: create, get, list, update, delete, describe, logs, exec\n182: \n183: - [ ] **TASK-061**: Create `pkg/cli/codeinterpreter/list.go`\n184:   - Implement `NewCodeInterpreterListCommand(o *codeInterpreterOptions) *cobra.Command`\n185:   - Similar to agentruntime list\n186: \n187: - [ ] **TASK-062**: Create `pkg/cli/codeinterpreter/get.go`\n188:   - Implement `NewCodeInterpreterGetCommand(o *codeInterpreterOptions) *cobra.Command`\n189: \n190: - [ ] **TASK-063**: Create `pkg/cli/codeinterpreter/describe.go`\n191:   - Implement `NewCodeInterpreterDescribeCommand(o *codeInterpreterOptions) *cobra.Command`\n192: \n193: - [ ] **TASK-064**: Create `pkg/cli/codeinterpreter/create.go`\n194:   - Implement `NewCodeInterpreterCreateCommand(o *codeInterpreterOptions) *cobra.Command`\n195:   - Flags: --runtime, --namespace, --cpu, --memory, --image\n196: \n197: - [ ] **TASK-065**: Create `pkg/cli/codeinterpreter/update.go`\n198:   - Implement `Ne